        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer541255336" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3250876536644101688">Last time I reviewed a Robotham novel I wasn&apos;t very impressed. The author had a great writing style but the character, a whiney psychiatrist, was unlikeable. I&apos;m glad I persevered! This time the main character was adorable! Alisha is very driven with external goals and some hidden internal motivations that she has not yet revealed even to herself. She is a modern girl who also tries accommodate some of her Sikh traditions. The drama is high, with death, black market child adoption, and the ensla</span>
  <span id="freeText3250876536644101688" style="display:none">Last time I reviewed a Robotham novel I wasn't very impressed. The author had a great writing style but the character, a whiney psychiatrist, was unlikeable. I'm glad I persevered! This time the main character was adorable! Alisha is very driven with external goals and some hidden internal motivations that she has not yet revealed even to herself. She is a modern girl who also tries accommodate some of her Sikh traditions. The drama is high, with death, black market child adoption, and the enslaving of young women. I'll be back for more!</span>
  <a data-text-id="3250876536644101688" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

