        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1978491535" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2190254232922072819">A bit of a disappointing read, since I had loved <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/25674405.Life_or_Death' title='Life or Death by Michael Robotham' rel='nofollow noopener'>Life or Death</a>.<br/><br/>I found the novel to be long in places that I didn&apos;t want it to be and it wasn&apos;t long enough in some other places. I wasn&apos;t a fan reading about the sex trafficking and slavery aspect and I wished there was more time spent on the ending and how everything came to be at the end. </span>
  <span id="freeText2190254232922072819" style="display:none">A bit of a disappointing read, since I had loved <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/25674405.Life_or_Death" title="Life or Death by Michael Robotham" rel="nofollow noopener">Life or Death</a>.<br /><br />I found the novel to be long in places that I didn't want it to be and it wasn't long enough in some other places. I wasn't a fan reading about the sex trafficking and slavery aspect and I wished there was more time spent on the ending and how everything came to be at the end. </span>
