<div id="review_1844509788" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1844509788" />
    <a title="Calzean" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/26416859-calzean"><img alt="Calzean" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1469230411p2/26416859.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1844509788?book_show_action=true">Jul 22, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Calzean" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Calzean" href="/user/show/26416859-calzean">Calzean</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9780316252287" href="/book/show/25530397-the-night-ferry">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/26416859-calzean?shelf=author-australia">author-australia</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/26416859-calzean?shelf=culture-afghanistan">culture-afghanistan</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/26416859-calzean?shelf=culture-netherlands">culture-netherlands</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/26416859-calzean?shelf=crime-thriller-mystery">crime-thriller-mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/26416859-calzean?shelf=culture-england">culture-england</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1844509788" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17303696741044063581">Robotham is one of the best of the modern crime writers. Within the first few pages of this book, there is an 8 month pregnant woman who is not pregnant who is killed in a hit and run. The driver of taxi has been dead for years. And Alisha Singh, a 29 year old Sikh policewoman is wondering what is happening.<br/>Then there is people smuggling, forced pregnancies of refugees who are paid to provide surrogate children to desperate couples, murders, IRA link, prostitution and shady characters. It&apos;s a pa</span>
  <span id="freeText17303696741044063581" style="display:none">Robotham is one of the best of the modern crime writers. Within the first few pages of this book, there is an 8 month pregnant woman who is not pregnant who is killed in a hit and run. The driver of taxi has been dead for years. And Alisha Singh, a 29 year old Sikh policewoman is wondering what is happening.<br />Then there is people smuggling, forced pregnancies of refugees who are paid to provide surrogate children to desperate couples, murders, IRA link, prostitution and shady characters. It's a page turner but one that questions the ethics of adoption, the fragility of life faced by orphans in war-torn nations and the inequality of life.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17303696741044063581" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


